Finsen, Hanne: Matisse, Rouveyre: correspondance. Flammarion, 2001. ISBN 9782080101839. 
Flam, Jack: Matisse and Picasso: The Story of Their Rivalry and Friendship. Basic Books, 2008. ISBN 9780786723836. 
Flam, Jack D.: Matisse on Art. University of California Press, 1995. ISBN 9780520200326. 
Gowing, Lawrence: Matisse. Thames and Hudson, 1979. ISBN 9780500181713. 
Müller, Karin: Métamorphoses de Matisse: Roman d'une vie. Editions Guéna-Barley, 2013. ISBN 9782919058068. 
Percheron, René & Brouder, Christian: Matisse: de la couleur à l'architecture. Citadelles & Mazenod, 2002. ISBN 978-2850881824. 
Russell, John: The World of Matisse: 1869–1954. Time Life Books, 1969. 
Russell, John: Matisse: Father and Son. Harry N. Abrams, 2001. ISBN 9780810929913. 
